  "prompt": "Where can I download free pdf books for mechanical engineering?",
  "response": "There are several websites where you can find free PDF books for mechanical engineering. Here are some legitimate and legal options:\n\n1. **Open Textbook Library**: This site offers a variety of free, peer-reviewed, and openly licensed textbooks, including those for mechanical engineering. [Open Textbook Library](https://open.umn.edu/opentextbooks)\n\n2. **Project Gutenberg**: While primarily focused on literature, you might find some older engineering texts here. [Project Gutenberg](https://www.gutenberg.org/)\n\n3. **Google Books**: Google Books provides free access to many books, including some textbooks. You can search for specific titles or topics in mechanical engineering. [Google Books](https://books.google.com/)\n\n4. **Internet Archive**: This digital library offers free access to millions of books, including engineering texts. You can search for mechanical engineering books and download them in PDF format. [Internet Archive](https://archive.org/)\n\n5. **LibreTexts**: This open-access platform offers a wide range of free textbooks, including some for engineering disciplines. [LibreTexts](https://eng.libretexts.org/)\n\n6. **Free-Ebooks.net**: This site offers a variety of free ebooks in different categories, including engineering. You might find some mechanical engineering books here. [Free-Ebooks.net](https://www.free-ebooks.net/)\n\n7. **Bookboon**: This site provides free textbooks for students and professionals, including engineering subjects. However, they might ask for your email address to download the books. [Bookboon](https://bookboon.com/)\n\n8. **MIT OpenCourseWare**: While not a traditional book site, MIT OpenCourseWare provides free access to course materials, including lecture notes and textbooks, for various engineering courses. [MIT OpenCourseWare](https://ocw.mit.edu/)\n\n9. **OnlineProgrammingBooks**: This site offers free books and tutorials on a wide range of topics, including mechanical engineering. [OnlineProgrammingBooks](https://www.onlineprogrammingbooks.com/)\n\n10. **HathiTrust Digital Library**: This digital library offers free access to millions of books, including some on mechanical engineering. [HathiTrust Digital Library](https://www.hathitrust.org/)\n\nAlways ensure that the books you download are legally available for free and respect copyright laws. Some websites may offer pirated content, which is illegal and unethical. Stick to trusted sources like the ones listed above.",
